---
import PublicLayout from '../../../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Training"
  description="Practical agile training from smagile. ProKanban accredited courses and bespoke agile fundamentals workshops."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">Training</h1>

    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-200">
      Our training is built on over a decade of supporting product teams. Every course
      focuses on real-world application, not just theory. Your people will leave with skills
      they can put into practice immediately.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8">
      <a
        href="/how-we-help/training/prokanban/"
        class="block p-8 bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-grey-800 rounded-xl border border-secondary-200 dark:border-grey-700 hover:border-primary dark:hover:border-secondary transition-colors"
      >
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">
          Applying Professional Kanban (APK)
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-200">
          Licensed by ProKanban.org. Learn to apply kanban principles to improve flow,
          reduce bottlenecks, and deliver more predictably.
        </p>
        <span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-primary dark:text-secondary font-medium">
          Learn more
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/how-we-help/training/agile-fundamentals/"
        class="block p-8 bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-grey-800 rounded-xl border border-secondary-200 dark:border-grey-700 hover:border-primary dark:hover:border-secondary transition-colors"
      >
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">
          Agile Fundamentals
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-200">
          Bespoke training for teams and leaders at any stage of their agile journey.
          From foundational principles to advanced practices.
        </p>
        <span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-primary dark:text-secondary font-medium">
          Learn more
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
